 《鬣狗》取消后《全面战争》开发商将专注于策略游戏https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-developer-will-focus-on-strategy-games-after-hyenas-cancellation-3551360?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=total-war-鬣狗取消后开发商将专注于策略游戏Ryan EasbyThu, 30 Nov 2023 14:56:07 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3551360 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="鬣狗。图片来源：创意大会。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该消息来自一份财务报告</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-developer-will-focus-on-strategy-games-after-hyenas-cancellation-3551360">《鬣狗》被取消后，《全面战争》的开发商将专注于策略游戏</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="鬣狗。图片来源：创意大会。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Hyenas-cancelled-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>世嘉宣布， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/total-war">《全面战争》</a></em>开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/creative-assembly">Creative Assembly</a>在取消<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/hyenas">《鬣狗》</a>后，未来将专注于策略游戏。</em></p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/boss-level-2023-amelia-tyler-baldurs-gate-3-3550385">《博德之门 3》如何让叙述者阿米莉亚·泰勒度过“非常黑暗的时期”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/sega">SEGA</a>总裁兼首席执行官 Haruki Satomi <a href="https://www.segasammy.co.jp/cms/wp-content/uploads/pdf/en/ir/20231108_q2_presentation_with_scripts_e.pdf">最近的业绩报告</a>中，该公司透露，计划让 Creative Assembly 重新关注 RTS（即时战略）游戏，同时进一步深入解释<em>《鬣狗》</em>被取消的原因。</p><p> “Creative Assembly 擅长 RTS 类型的离线游戏，但他们接受了开发<em>鬣狗的挑战，”</em>里美说。</p><p> “虽然游戏很好，但我们决定取消<em>《鬣狗》</em>的开发，因为当我们考虑是否真的可以将其作为竞技网络游戏长期运营时，我们认为它无法达到让我们的用户满意的质量。 ”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3506557" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3506557" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3506557" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/creative-assembly-hyenas-cancellation-leads-to-layoffs.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/creative-assembly-hyenas-cancellation-leads-to-layoffs.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/creative-assembly-hyenas-cancellation-leads-to-layoffs-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/creative-assembly-hyenas-cancellation-leads-to-layoffs-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/creative-assembly-hyenas-cancellation-leads-to-layoffs-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/creative-assembly-hyenas-cancellation-leads-to-layoffs-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/creative-assembly-hyenas-cancellation-leads-to-layoffs-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3506557" class="wp-caption-text"> “鬣狗”图片来源：创意大会</figcaption></figure><p>在讨论SEGA工作室的结构改革时，报告列出SEGA计划“专注于每个工作室的优势并缩小阵容”，而Creative Assembly则专注于与之前的<em>《全面战争》</em>游戏类似的游戏。</p><p> <em>《鬣狗》</em>和几款未宣布的游戏于 9 月被取消，负责该游戏的开发团队也进行了多次裁员。该报告对此进行了更深入的探讨，Satomi 指出：</p><p> “我们决定取消一些游戏的开发，包括<em>《鬣狗》</em>和其他未宣布的游戏。因此，我们对在建工作进行了减记。此外，我们一直致力于通过减少 Creative Assembly 的办公室和员工人数来优化固定成本。”</p><p>然而，目前完全不知道世嘉还取消了哪些游戏，除了<em>《鬣狗》之外，没有任何关于正在开发的游戏的声明。</em></p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/metal-hellsinger">《Metal: Hellsinger》</a></em>透露了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/trivium">Trivium</a>的 Matt Heafy 的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/metal-hellsinger-reveals-loud-new-track-from-triviums-matt-heafy-3551339">全新曲目</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/total-war-developer-will-focus-on-strategy-games-after-hyenas-cancellation-3551360">《鬣狗》被取消后，《全面战争》的开发商将专注于策略游戏</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ;
